sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Web Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant AUTH as Auth Service
    participant USER as User Service
    participant MATCH as Matching Service
    participant REC as Recommendation Service
    participant CHAT as Chat Service
    participant MOD as Moderation Service

    UI->>GW: GET /api/dashboard/user-1
    GW->>USER: Fetch profile + flags
    GW->>MATCH: Fetch matches
    GW->>REC: Fetch recommendations
    GW->>CHAT: Fetch conversations
    GW->>MOD: Fetch anonymous feed
    GW-->>UI: Aggregated dashboard payload

    UI->>CHAT: WebSocket room join
    CHAT-->>UI: message.created
    CHAT-->>UI: presence.updated
